        "Description": "Miami’s high-speed race hides a deadly conspiracy. Ted Mendez leaks Kronstadt’s top-secret tech to the highest bidder. Fishy Joe floods the event with fake VIP passes, letting criminals slip past security unnoticed. Reed Oliver, a rogue engineer, sabotages Sierra Knox’s prototype car, risking catastrophic failure. Eliminate all three silently and without witnesses. Failure means chaos. Stay sharp, 47. Good hunting.",
